WEBVTT

00:07:56.120 --> 00:08:00.050
and we believe it’s true because you have
done enough research and thought over it,

00:08:00.074 --> 00:08:01.890
how do we bring this into practice?

00:08:01.914 --> 00:08:05.200
How? I believe what you are saying

00:08:05.200 --> 00:08:08.200
but how do I really believe
that I am not permanent?

00:08:08.200 --> 00:08:09.576
Because I am…

00:08:09.600 --> 00:08:10.477
AA: You are right.

00:08:10.477 --> 00:08:13.920
SRK: Tell us, the people 
sitting here and at homes,

00:08:13.920 --> 00:08:15.480
how to practically follow this?

00:08:15.480 --> 00:08:20.016
AA: First of all, I’d like to say
that this is not my advice.

00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:25.096
A lot of people have thought over it,
I’m only bringing their stories here.

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:27.879
SRK: Don’t worry. We won't not
hold you responsible.

00:08:27.879 --> 00:08:31.736
AA: So Gautama Buddha was telling
us this 2,500 years ago,